Word Frequency ${project.version}

PRE-REQUESITES
- JDK 1.8 or above

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
1. Extract the zip to install location.
2. Check that the extract folder has the bin, config, lib folders available.
3. This will be the home path for the application.

CONFIGURATION
1. Ready the seed file as well as the files indicated in the seed file(Ensure that application has read access rights to it)
2. Goto home directory
3. Goto config
4. Edit the application.properties

STARTING

1. Goto home directory
2. Goto bin
3. Run start.cmd

RUNNING WORD SEARCH

Once application is deployed go to http://<hostname>:<port>/search?word=<wordToSearch>

Output is in json format